Name: Relief fragment with cartouche of Sethos I (or II ?)
Description: Relief fragment with the cartouche of Sethos I (or II ?). More or less following the contours of the cartouche, this piece has been taken out of its original context. The inscription is in raised relief and is white of colour outside the cartouche. The ring is green (?), the interior of the cartouche yellow. The lower end has broken away.
